1
00:01:35,990 --> 00:01:38,280
[Too Young To Love]

2
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:41,110
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:46,870
Wake up.

4
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:55,350
My name is Yi Lan.

5
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:58,840
Today is the first day
of my sophomore year of high school.

6
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:02,290
This is my neighbor, Tong Xiaole.

7
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,160
By the way,

8
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,000
I'm also...

9
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,710
an excellent cellist.

10
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,170
Cutting it close again.

11
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:37,520
Sister,

12
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:39,960
are you going to a cello competition?

13
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,120
No, no, no.

14
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:44,800
Is Xiaole going with you?

15
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,400
Yes!

16
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,120
Hurry up and eat something first.

17
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,120
There's no time!

18
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,840
Why are you carrying your cello?

19
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,840
For the school orchestra audition.

20
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,360
You haven't even figured out your studies.

21
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,370
-I'm leaving!
-Be careful!

22
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,430
Coming! Coming!

23
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,080
Let's go!

24
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:05,960
Tong Xiaole!

25
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,320
You're not waiting for me again!

26
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,000
[Class 9, Grade 11]

27
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,840
Just this one sentence.

28
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,800
Remember this key point.

29
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,330
Alright, class dismissed.

30
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,530
Class Representative,
wipe the blackboard.

31
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,430
Mr. Bu.

32
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:24,150
Well, I've prepared my cello piece.

33
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,430
When is the audition?

34
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,280
There's too much on my plate
with the start of the semester.

35
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,400
I forgot about that matter.

36
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:32,000
Well, your application
was indeed submitted by me.

37
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,079
But I'm not in charge of the orchestra.

38
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,079
You know that too.

39
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:35,840
They...

40
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,680
Well, they...

41
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,840
It seems they've chosen someone else.

42
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,040
Chosen someone else?

43
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,870
Who?

44
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,560
Wait a moment.

45
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,000
Um...

46
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,560
Luo Ningzi?

47
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,400
Mm.

48
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:07,960
Go in first.

49
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,590
We'll talk later. We'll talk later.

50
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:09,120
Come! Come!

51
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,560
Come!

52
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,560
Come!

53
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,000
Sorry to take up your break time!

54
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,000
Go back to your seats, everyone!

55
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,960
Sit down, everyone.

56
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,240
Let me introduce someone to you.

57
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,430
This is our new transfer student,

58
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,920
Luo Ningzi.

59
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,390
Luo Ningzi,

60
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,420
introduce yourself to everyone.

61
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,680
Hello, everyone, my name is Luo Ningzi.

62
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,520
Give her a warm welcome.

63
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,750
That should be the only empty seat
in our class now.

64
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:38,630
Sit there for now.

65
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,800
We'll rotate seats later.

66
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,360
Okay?

67
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,430
Help each other out, okay?

68
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,430
-Okay.
-Okay.

69
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:47,610
Chinese class.

70
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,360
Class begins.

71
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:01,360
Stand up!

72
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:04,830
-Hello, sir.
-Hello, sir.

73
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,530
Sit down.

74
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,310
Lan,

75
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:37,230
so you can't join the orchestra?

76
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:42,240
She must have been handpicked.

77
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,750
It's fine.

78
00:05:50,270 --> 00:05:51,830
She's going to the school orchestra later.

79
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:52,560
I'll go take a look.

80
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,490
I'll go with you.

81
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,870
You guys plan to skip self-study class?

82
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:56,750
Count me in.

83
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,159
Xiaole, are you going?

84
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:58,960
Are you going?

85
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:00,830
I'm not interested.

86
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:01,630
So I'll pass.

87
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,190
We meet again,

88
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,120
Tong Xiaole.

89
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:21,390
The way Luo Ningzi looks at Tong Xiaole...

90
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:22,870
Something's off.

91
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:25,670
Did they know each other before?

92
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:27,510
How is that possible?

93
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,920
I grew up with Tong Xiaole.

94
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,050
How would I not know?

95
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,560
Why is Zhao Zhenghao so handsome?

96
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,480
And he studies conducting.

97
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:10,890
Don't you think so?

98
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,390
She is indeed good-looking.

99
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,510
And she plays well.

100
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,880
Points-Deductor Hu will be here soon.

101
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:29,870
Get lost.

102
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:45,360
Director Hu.

103
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:46,560
Director... Director...

104
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,390
Director Hu. Director Hu.

105
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:47,880
Director Hu.

106
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,240
Director Hu.

107
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:48,800
Director Hu.

108
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,659
D-Director Hu.

109
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:54,440
Tong Xiaole from Class 9, Grade 11.

110
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:56,430
Chen Fan from Class 9, Grade 11.

111
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:58,190
Yi Lan from Class 9, Grade 11.

112
00:07:58,310 --> 00:08:00,310
Qiao Mengmeng from Class 9, Grade 11.

113
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,430
Qiao Mengmeng.

114
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:03,870
These two strands of hair
on your forehead are too long.

115
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:05,130
Cut them immediately!

116
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:06,270
Yi Lan.

117
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,070
You're at the bottom of the rankings.

118
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,470
You're always involved.

119
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,630
Chen Fan.

120
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,370
Why wear glasses without lenses?

121
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,800
And look at your clothes.

122
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,680
Sloppy.

123
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,630
Tong Xiaole.

124
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:25,830
Top of the grade.

125
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:26,720
Keep it up.

126
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:29,040
Don't let them lead you astray.

127
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,929
You three, each of you
loses one point for your class!

128
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,960
The four of us are in the same class.

129
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,720
I know!

130
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,809
So your class

131
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,059
will lose 3 points!

132
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,120
I'll deal with you later.

133
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,550
Points deducted again.

134
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,600
What's wrong with having bad grades?

135
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,440
Why didn't he scold Tong Xiaole?

136
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,650
What did you say?

137
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,910
It wasn't me.

138
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:06,750
Where is he?

139
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,920
Why isn't he here yet?

140
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,280
What a coincidence.

141
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,790
I happen to have a question for you.

142
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,790
How did you know Luo Ningzi?

143
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,080
Why have you never told me about that?

144
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,840
She plays the cello so well.

145
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,080
It's a bit windy today.

146
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,740
I need to go home early.

147
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,140
Are you going to tell me or not?

148
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,440
Luo Ningzi and I

149
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:50,150
met at a tutoring class.

150
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:53,540
Just like you,
she's played the cello since childhood.

151
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,790
She's taken part in many competitions.

152
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:57,320
The only difference is

153
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,930
she has won many national championships.

154
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,320
Then why did she transfer to our school?

155
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:11,790
Do you know the High School
Affiliated to Music Conservatory?

156
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:13,080
It's full of talented people.

157
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,610
The competition is fierce.

158
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,960
Maybe she thinks it's...

159
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,440
easier to apply for studying abroad
from our school,

160
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,840
so she transferred here.

161
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,720
If I get a chance...

162
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,550
I must ask her for advice.

163
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:28,680
Learn a thing or two.

164
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,660
Learning to play the cello

165
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:35,670
requires a good learning environment
and family support.

166
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:36,440
It's okay.

167
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:38,480
You've already worked very hard.

168
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,280
You're great.

169
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,270
I know.

170
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,150
Let's go.

171
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,790
The novel Shan ordered for me has arrived.

172
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,550
Let's go to the musical instrument store.

173
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,950
Alright. Get on the bike.

174
00:10:52,550 --> 00:10:53,440
Let's go!

175
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:56,790
Tong Xiaole,

176
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,850
what are you doing?

177
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:58,550
You...

178
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,080
Tong Xiaole!

179
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,200
Miss,

180
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:06,960
where is Shan?

181
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,790
Shan went to restock.

182
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:09,790
He left it on the fifth shelf for you.

183
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,440
My dad is making me
something delicious tonight.

184
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,790
Come to my place for dinner.

185
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:43,360
No.

186
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:45,210
I need to take photos tonight.

187
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,200
Boring.

188
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,150
Take photos. Come.

189
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:07,960
Are we in the frame?

190
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,720
Did you get the shot?

191
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,550
Hurry, hurry.

192
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:31,870
[Xiaole, I transferred you 1,000 yuan
for living expenses.]

193
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:36,420
[Tell me if it's not enough. Your dad
and I will be home a few days late.]

194
00:12:42,890 --> 00:12:45,270
[My life's piece:]

195
00:12:45,290 --> 00:12:54,590
[Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2,
3rd Movement]

196
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:51,570
It always brings tears to my eyes,
no matter when.

197
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,240
Someone actually

198
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:57,600
has the exact same life piece as me.

199
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,650
If I could become friends with her,

200
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,670
we could not only practice together

201
00:13:02,670 --> 00:13:04,130
but also talk about music.

202
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:05,790
That would be amazing.

203
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:08,080
[Nickname: Ning]

204
00:13:08,130 --> 00:13:11,140
[Friend Request] [Hello, I'm Yi Lan.]

205
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:12,140
[Sending]

206
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:18,550
Yi Lan.

207
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:20,480
You're back.

208
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,840
Did you skip a meal again?

209
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,670
I brought you a feast.

210
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,670
Let's go.

211
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,000
Open the door.

212
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:42,600
Tell me.

213
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:44,640
Waiting at my door at this hour—

214
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,240
did Uncle Dong

215
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,620
tell you to stop playing the cello again?

216
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:57,120
What life photos did you take today?

217
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,080
Let me see.

218
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,700
There indeed are some.

219
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,970
Swipe right. Right?

220
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:12,720
Your photography skills are amazing!

221
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,840
Even better than the ones I see

222
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:17,170
in professional photography magazines.

223
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,850
Such a waste as just a hobby.

224
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:20,960
You should participate
in a grand competition.

225
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,600
Maybe you'll win a big prize.

226
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,800
By the way,

227
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,600
when will your parents
come back this time?

228
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:31,790
They are

229
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,560
focused on making money now.

230
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,240
They deliver renovation materials
every day.

231
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:37,970
They only remember
they have a son occasionally.

232
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,670
Now I feel like

233
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,680
I'm just a distant relative.

234
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,960
You still have me.

235
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,440
I'm

236
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,720
just a call away.

237
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:49,480
And don't be shy
about coming to my place for meals.

238
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,740
We have plenty of food.

239
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,480
And don't always

240
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,720
ride your bike

241
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,200
all alone.

242
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,480
Take me with you.

243
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:00,910
I'll consider it.

244
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:12,400
[Ning
Friend request rejected]

245
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:12,520
Luo Ningzi rejected my friend request.

246
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:15,290
Why did you take the initiative
to add her?

247
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,960
I want to play a cello duet with her.

248
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,790
Then you deserve it.

249
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:35,910
Mom,

250
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,960
have you... and Dad eaten today?

251
00:16:55,410 --> 00:17:03,930
[Sleep on time.
Don't stay up playing games.]

252
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:22,609
[Are you there?] [Yes.]

253
00:17:22,609 --> 00:17:30,310
[She really has been practicing hard.]

254
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:34,920
Um...

255
00:17:35,310 --> 00:17:35,830
I...

256
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:39,070
I think studies should come first now.

257
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,350
Sorry.

258
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:46,950
[Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2]

259
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:50,640
-What are you doing?
-What are you doing?

260
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:52,030
Don't distract me from serious business.

261
00:17:52,030 --> 00:17:53,090
Serious business?

262
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:54,810
This is serious business?

263
00:17:55,830 --> 00:17:57,000
Stand here and keep watch for me.

264
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,130
Don't let anyone in.

265
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,350
Who is this letter for?

266
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:15,190
You'll know soon enough.

267
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:20,590
You're so eager
to join the school orchestra.

268
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:22,400
Do you have a crush on someone?

269
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:28,590
Who uses such a cheesy way
to confess nowadays?

270
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:28,610
[Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2]

271
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,330
You don't understand.

272
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:31,830
I wrote this stroke by stroke.

273
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:33,090
It's all from my heart.

274
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,410
Cheesy, cheesy.

275
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:42,750
Here.

276
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:44,350
Someone's here!

277
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,280
Hurry, let's go!

278
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:46,270
Where to?

279
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:49,400
Wait!

280
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:50,790
Hide!

281
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:52,110
Why hide?

282
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:55,930
Luo Ningzi.

283
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,550
You just joined the orchestra.

284
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:59,310
It's okay if you don't understand.

285
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:01,310
I've already found you a good partner

286
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,570
to practice together.

287
00:19:06,350 --> 00:19:07,280
I don't need one.

288
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:10,110
She really is quite cold.

289
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,510
I'm the captain of the school orchestra.

290
00:19:14,510 --> 00:19:15,640
I have the final say.

291
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:18,750
I have a fixed practice schedule

292
00:19:18,750 --> 00:19:20,080
and a practice teacher.

293
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:26,630
What's wrong?

294
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,560
Are you not feeling well?

295
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:32,520
Someone's here.

296
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:36,640
We're playing hide-and-seek.

297
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,590
Can't you tell?

298
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:38,920
Luo Ningzi.

299
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,640
That video I sent you last night...

300
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:42,310
I saw it.

301
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:46,350
I know you two are very close.

302
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,070
But with me,

303
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:48,600
only ability counts.

304
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:50,850
Her cello skills aren't good enough.

305
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:54,250
She started playing at five just like you.

306
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:58,680
She was the national cello champion
in the kindergarten category for 3 years.

307
00:19:59,240 --> 00:19:59,590
You don't have to

308
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:01,400
act so high and mighty.

309
00:20:02,750 --> 00:20:03,550
So what?

310
00:20:04,590 --> 00:20:05,880
Things from childhood—

311
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,510
how long will you talk about that?

312
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:08,510
You know very well

313
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,840
what her skill level is.

314
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:10,880
I do know.

315
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:13,510
She's the best in the world.

316
00:20:14,270 --> 00:20:15,510
Luo Ningzi?

317
00:20:16,270 --> 00:20:17,590
You've only been here for a few days

318
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:20,320
and you already
know the top student of our grade?

319
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:23,560
[Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2]

320
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,720
This must be a love letter

321
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:27,790
-Give it to me!
-for our boss from some girl.

322
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,240
Give it to me!

323
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:30,070
-I really like your performance
-Tong Xiaole, help me get it back!

324
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:32,480
of Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2.

325
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:34,000
Is it that funny?

326
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:38,030
Junior.

327
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,840
[To Luo Ningzi]

328
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:39,960
Since you like me,

329
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:41,310
just give it to me in person.
Why did you...

330
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:42,310
It's not for you!

331
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:44,430
-Narcissist.
-Narcissist.

332
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:54,310
Thanks.

333
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:02,110
But I didn't come to this school

334
00:21:02,110 --> 00:21:03,310
to make friends.

335
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:04,960
[Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2]

336
00:21:07,770 --> 00:21:09,510
[Rachmaninoff's Symphony No. 2]

337
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,680
It's easy to buy this.

338
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:24,270
I can buy you a new one.

339
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:26,280
It's not easy to buy this.

340
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,310
This is a collector's edition record

341
00:21:27,310 --> 00:21:29,640
I've collected since elementary school.

342
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:40,070
I'm sorry.

343
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:42,230
I need to go practice.

344
00:21:42,830 --> 00:21:43,550
And...

345
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,460
you've never heard me play in person.

346
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:49,120
How can you assume...

347
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:51,240
I'm not worthy of being your friend?

348
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,590
Play.

349
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:18,550
F-Fine, I'll play.

350
00:22:40,830 --> 00:22:42,360
Do you have the sheet music?

351
00:23:01,270 --> 00:23:02,590
Paganini's Caprices.

352
00:23:07,310 --> 00:23:08,960
Paganini's Caprices?

353
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,000
They are very difficult.

354
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:11,310
Can you play them?

355
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:34,030
Do you have rosin?

356
00:25:06,030 --> 00:25:07,760
I'll definitely fix it for you.

357
00:25:10,110 --> 00:25:11,170
It's her. It's her.

358
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:22,000
Don't bother fixing it.

359
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,930
It definitely won't play anymore.

360
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:33,960
Let me tell you.

361
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,720
Luo Ningzi looked furious.

362
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:38,940
If I hadn't stepped in,
they'd definitely have fought.

363
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,720
And Yi Lan is really weird.

364
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:46,800
She wrote a letter to a girl.

365
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:54,720
But Yi Lan's performance
was indeed average.

366
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:55,270
Yeah.

367
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:01,370
Zhao Zhenghao.

368
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:03,750
Sorry.

369
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:05,440
I didn't expect to bump into you.

370
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,750
We were just playing a game.

371
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:07,750
I apologize to you.

372
00:26:07,750 --> 00:26:08,400
I'm sorry.

373
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:10,160
I hope you can forgive me.

374
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:11,960
Sorry. Sorry.

375
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:16,070
What is that about?

376
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:16,830
Strange.

377
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:25,070
The machine is broken.

378
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:25,930
Zhao Zhenghao!

379
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:28,040
What are you looking for?

380
00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:29,310
Looking for this?

381
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,110
-It's her?
-It's her.

382
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,440
The one in the video.

383
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:37,270
Is that her?

384
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:38,270
It's her. It's her.

385
00:26:38,270 --> 00:26:39,070
What are you looking at?

386
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:40,800
Go back to your own classrooms!

387
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:48,920
Lan,

388
00:26:49,270 --> 00:26:51,870
the video of you
playing the cello is trending.

389
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:54,270
Don't be too upset.

390
00:26:54,830 --> 00:26:57,630
Actually,
everyone really sympathizes with you.

391
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:59,030
What's there to be upset about?

392
00:26:59,030 --> 00:27:01,400
I indeed haven't been playing the cello
as long as she has.

393
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,400
Exactly.

394
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:06,880
If you practiced longer, you definitely
would have played better than her.

395
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:19,830
Let's go eat barbecue later.

396
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:22,240
I found a place
that offers insanely spicy food.

397
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:25,480
My treat—dinner, karaoke, claw machine.

398
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,200
I'm not going.

399
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:30,050
My dad asked me
to go home for dinner tonight.

400
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:32,110
Mengmeng, I'm almost done.

401
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,060
I'm leaving first.

402
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:35,110
Have fun.

403
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,060
I'm leaving first.

404
00:28:11,750 --> 00:28:12,950
Still not going home?

405
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:27,070
I know. It's very embarrassing.

406
00:28:28,070 --> 00:28:29,680
I'm already so upset.

407
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:32,540
Can you stop saying such harsh words?

408
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,000
This time...

409
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:09,550
what wish do you want to write?

410
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:13,100
[Everyone, just forget it.]

411
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:15,720
Writing wishes on candy wrappers

412
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,590
is just a marketing gimmick.

413
00:29:17,590 --> 00:29:18,850
None of your business!

414
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,070
It will come true!

415
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:44,510
Tell me,

416
00:29:45,310 --> 00:29:46,830
do I still have a chance?

417
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:50,930
How old are you?

418
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:52,440
Fifteen.

419
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,550
Exactly.

420
00:29:53,590 --> 00:29:54,720
You're only 15.

421
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:56,440
Anything is possible.

422
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,510
I'm 15, and she's 15 too!

423
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:01,480
I'm working hard,
and she's working hard too!

424
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,070
I'll never catch up to her!

425
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,590
Who exactly is Luo Ningzi to you?

426
00:30:06,590 --> 00:30:08,920
Why do you
have to compare yourself to her?

427
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:10,790
I envy her!

428
00:30:10,790 --> 00:30:11,880
I'm jealous of her!

429
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:16,110
We both play the cello.

430
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:19,960
Why is the gap so huge?

431
00:30:23,270 --> 00:30:25,160
I'm so envious.

432
00:30:25,350 --> 00:30:27,110
I'm so envious!

433
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:33,510
I don't think the gap is that huge.

434
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:36,550
Sometimes, I think
your performance is even...

435
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:37,070
Shut up!

436
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,070
I know.

437
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:46,030
Jealousy is a terrible force.

438
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:48,520
I don't want to be jealous of her.

439
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:50,270
I want her to respect me

440
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,720
and be friends with me.

441
00:31:06,070 --> 00:31:07,470
Which class are you from?

442
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,240
Mr. Hu! Mr. Hu!

443
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,270
-Run!
-What?

444
00:31:10,270 --> 00:31:10,880
Let's go!

445
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:12,830
Stop right there!

446
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:13,550
Wait for me!

447
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:13,880
Stop!

448
00:31:14,510 --> 00:31:15,510
Wait for me!

449
00:31:20,460 --> 00:31:27,460
[Photographer]
